data.description: $10,000 Seller Concession!!! Modern contemporary home located within the Trinity River Corridor just minutes from Downtown Dallas, Dart Rail station, and Dallas Zoo. Upgraded home with Fully encapsulated foam insulation throughout the house including roof and attic space which means more efficient heating and cooling. Energy efficient windows and doors. Breathtaking Downtown Dallas View at the top of the staircase and balcony. OPEN FLOOR PLAN, designer kitchen with large island, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances. Abundant natural light. Spacious fenced in backyard with covered patio.
